title: The Pets Table - Fresh Large Box  7 x 15.7oz Chicken & 7 x 14.6oz Beef & 7 x 16.9oz Turkey
description: Human grade fresh dog food which is gently cooked to preserve the essential nutrients. Recipes are then flash frozen and delivered straight to your door ready for your pup to lick the bowl clean - expect a paw of approval. Made in the USA, with the world’s finest ingredients. All recipes are developed with vets and are AAFCO complete and balanced for all life stages and all sizes. Made with 100% real, whole ingredients. No artificial flavors, preservatives or fillers. Supports improved digestion, healthier skin, shinier coats, immunity and increased energy levels. Feeding & transition instructions included within your delivered box. Roughly 4 weeks of food for a 26Lb adult dog. This large variety box includes 7 packs of 15.7oz Chicken Casserole with Green Beans, 7 packs of 14.6oz Beef Stew with Carrots and 7 packs of 16.9oz Turkey Casserole with Broccoli. *Your order will ship separately in The Pets Table branded box and may not arrive on your scheduled weekly HelloFresh delivery date (shipping is included in the total price). Customization of bundles is not available at this time.

